        " خَيْرُ الْقَرْضِ مَا جَرَّ مَنْفَعَةً ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Bishr Bin Maslama, and someone else, from the one who informed him, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Ja’far<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The best loan is what attracts the benefits’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "3. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Bishr ibn Muslimah from more than one person who reported who has said the following: “Abu Ja‘far, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘The best loan is that which attracts benefits.’” "
        ]
      }
